    {
      "text": "A 28-year-old metalworker presents with gradual vision loss and a history of a metallic foreign body injury 4 months ago. Examination reveals iron deposits on Iris, rusty deposits on the lens and pigmentary changes in the retina. What is the most likely cause of his condition?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
